      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and has been treated with the utmost care since it was new. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep, mirror-like shine with no chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the leather is supple without any creases, and all technology and controls function perfectly. It has been garage-kept, never driven in harsh weather, and comes with a full service history from the dealership. For a buyer seeking a car that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory, this is the perfect specimen.",
