      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of uncompromising quality. This vehicle has been maintained to a fastidious standard, exhibiting a showroom-grade exterior and a cabin that reflects meticulous preservation. Every mechanical component operates with the precision intended by the original engineers. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector to acquire a vehicle in truly superlative condition.",
