      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 38
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! If you've been looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the showroom price tag, you\u2019ve found it! This beauty is in absolute pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks like it just rolled off the lot. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so there\u2019s not a single blemish to be found. The interior is spotless and it drives like an absolute dream. You really have to see it in person to believe how clean it is. Drop me a message and let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
