    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo in concours-level condition. This example features the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six, retaining its factory sequential twin-turbocharged configuration. The drivetrain is anchored by the bulletproof Getrag V160 six-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential. Mechanically, the vehicle is superlative; compression levels remain within factory specifications across all cylinders, and the cooling system has been meticulously maintained to prevent heat soak. The chassis exhibits zero structural fatigue, with all original spot welds intact and a pristine undercarriage. Riding on factory-spec alloy wheels with fresh rubber, this Supra delivers the precise turn-in and high-speed stability it was engineered for. An unmolested, collector-quality specimen for the discerning purist.",
